722393f-b.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 110th Street
722393f-b.text:
(1)
Park Avenue, west side, north from but not including 110th Street.
In the upper right hand corner may be seen the platform of
the New York and Harlem Railroad's 110th Street station, long
since fallen into disuse.
July 6, 1934.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, another view.
